{"tid":1301321,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日放榜既全部入撚晒黎","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T19:04:22.000Z","uid":217244,"like":27,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"39b67563c48dd9873ce179e523965c03a2b1bc69","tid":1301321,"uid":217244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"祝各位聽日放榜旗開得勝事事順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠分入想入嘅科目恭喜你<br />\n唔夠分入嘅都唔好氣餒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個過來人<br />\n我好推薦數底好又有修物理嘅人揀有關工程嘅科<br />\n因為讀工程真係好多好處<br />\n工程會成日俾人講到好多油頭毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坦白講而家啲工程科男女朋比例差唔多64咁濟<br />\n啲囡囡質素仲要唔差<br />\n我自己都食過兩條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連呂慧儀都係電子工程畢業<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔怕無工開<br />\n香港未來基建項目只升不減<br />\n工程師供不應求人工當然唔低得去邊<br />\n讀完四年假假地都係個工程師<br />\n仲要係專業人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係囡囡聽到都濕曬<br />\n<br />\n屌都係唔好講咁多廢事比人話假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望比左少少意見幫到大家<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908921f80b57558a1b9638ccc1f7002fcb532ec8","tid":1301321,"uid":217244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c048cc692fc4583bd4212a68b5d2a033b0fce89","tid":1301321,"uid":217244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"想多啲師弟妹見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349947d9fc4ab071f408cb6b1682e339b4cc4212","tid":1301321,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"連登 DSE 放榜抱抱團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\